do with the original YTS or YIFY group, but aims to take its place. As with the new EZTV, several large torrent sites are not allowing the group to use the YIFY or YTS brands on their sites.\r\n<div align="right">\r\n<h5>ALEXA RANK: 740 / COMPETE RANK: 4,271 / LAST YEAR #NA</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>10. <a href="http://torrentdownloads.me/">TORRENTDOWNLOADS</a></h4>\r\nTorrentDownloads has been around for several years. The torrent site regained a spot in the top 10 this year after it was featured for the last time in 2011. Its a no-nonsense index that provides torrents to millions of users each month.\r\n<div align="right">\r\n<h5>ALEXA RANK: 2,969 / LAST YEAR #NA</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<em>Disclaimer: Yes, we know that Alexa isnt perfect and that Compete has plenty of flaws, but when combined both do a pretty good job at comparing sites that operate in a similar niche.</em>', 'MOST POPULAR TORRENT SITES', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '412-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-03 20:07:40', '2016-10-03 20:07:40', '', 412, 'http://localhost/wptestsite/412-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
