(425, 4, '2016-10-05 18:02:13', '2016-10-05 18:02:13', '<h2>Hiccup solutions</h2>\r\nHiccup solutions:\r\n\r\nTake a deep breath.\r\nStart swallowing repeatedly while holding your breath.\r\nTry to get to 21 swallows before breathing again.\r\nIf you hiccup, start over.\r\nIf you cant get to 21 swallows in one breath, sip some water and sack up man! You can do it. Try again.', 'Hiccup solutions', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hiccup-solutions', '', '', '2016-10-05 18:02:13', '2016-10-05 18:02:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wptestsite/?p=425', 0, 'post', '', 0),
