(306, 1, '2016-09-08 17:42:47', '2016-09-08 17:42:47', '<h2>Alarm Clock,1103 Number Problem Solve</h2>\r\n<b>Problem Link :</b>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.urionlinejudge.com.br/judge/en/problems/view/1103"> https://www.urionlinejudge.com.br/judge/en/problems/view/1103</a>\r\n\r\n<b>Solution :</b>\r\n<div class="line number1 index0 alt2"><code class="c preprocessor">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number2 index1 alt1"><code class="c color1 bold">int</code> <code class="c plain">main()</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number3 index2 alt2"><code class="c plain">{</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number4 index3 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c color1 bold">int</code> <code class="c plain">h1,h2,m1,m2,min;</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number5 index4 alt2"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c keyword bold">while</code><code class="c plain">(1) {</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number6 index5 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c functions bold">scanf</code><code class="c plain">(</code><code class="c string">"%d %d %d %d"</code><code class="c plain">,&amp;h1,&amp;m1,&amp;h2,&amp;m2);</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number7 index6 alt2"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c keyword bold">if</code><code class="c plain">(h1==0&amp;&amp;h2==0&amp;&amp;m1==0&amp;&amp;m2==0)</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number8 index7 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c keyword bold">break</code><code class="c plain">;</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number9 index8 alt2"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c keyword bold">else</code> <code class="c keyword bold">if</code><code class="c plain">(h1&lt;h2 &amp;&amp; (m1==m2))</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number10 index9 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c plain">min = (h2-h1)*60;</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number11 index10 alt2"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c keyword bold">else</code> <code class="c keyword bold">if</code><code class="c plain">(h1&lt;h2 &amp;&amp; (m1&gt;m2))</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number12 index11 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c plain">min = (h2-h1)*60 - m1+m2;</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number13 index12 alt2"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c keyword bold">else</code> <code class="c keyword bold">if</code><code class="c plain">(h1&lt;h2 &amp;&amp; (m1&lt;m2))</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number14 index13 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c plain">min = (h2-h1)*60 + (m2-m1);</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number15 index14 alt2"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c keyword bold">else</code> <code class="c keyword bold">if</code><code class="c plain">(h1&gt;h2)</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number16 index15 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c plain">min = ((23-h1)*60+(60-m1))+(h2*60)+m2;</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number17 index16 alt2"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c keyword bold">else</code> <code class="c keyword bold">if</code><code class="c plain">(h1==h2 &amp;&amp; (m1&lt;=m2))</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number18 index17 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c plain">min = m2-m1;</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number19 index18 alt2"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c keyword bold">else</code> <code class="c keyword bold">if</code><code class="c plain">(h1==h2 &amp;&amp; (m1&gt;m2))</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number20 index19 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c plain">min = ((23-h1)*60+(60-m1))+(h2*60)+m2;</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number21 index20 alt2"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c functions bold">printf</code><code class="c plain">(</code><code class="c string">"%d\\n"</code><code class="c plain">,min);</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number22 index21 alt1"><code class="c spaces"></code><code class="c plain">}</code></div>\r\n<div class="line number23 index22 alt2"></div>\r\n<div class="line number24 index23 alt1"></div>\r\n<div class="line number25 index24 alt2"><code class="c plain">}</code></div>', '[Solve:] 1103 Number Problem [Alarm Clock] in Uri', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'solve-1103-number-problem-uri', '', '', '2016-09-08 18:10:24', '2016-09-08 18:10:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wptestsite/?p=306', 0, 'post', '', 0),
